### Claim Username - Create User and Battery
# This creates a new user with a unique username and initializes their daily battery
# Returns: userId, username, publicHash
# Sets: session cookie for authentication

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8081

### Claim new username
# @name claim
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/claim
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "Ev_Monday"
}

